quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  29,14,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuรช, i ugdud is. Izde$ yides, agim kkes ed smuset iseggwasen. Ibbwi ten uรชemmal, nitni d imednas"
  29,15,"Nsellek it, neppa akked wid iddan di lbabuรด. Nerra t d assekni i imavalen"
  29,16,"Ibรดahim, mi inna i ugdud is: \"รขabdet ร–ebbi, รชezzbet aS. Yif it wakka, i kunwi, lemmer teรฉรดim"
  29,17,"Tรขabdem kan tiรขancuรดin, war ร–ebbi. Tesnulfam d tikerkas. Ih, wid tรขabdem, war ร–ebbi, ur zmiren a kwen $iten. Ssutret l$it i ร–ebbi, รขabdet eP, snemmret aS. ยฃuรดeS ara tu$alem"
  29,18,"Ma tnekรดem, ihi, uqbel nnwen, nekรดen leoyus\". I iwatan, i umazan, siwa assiwev ubeggen"
  29,19,"Day ur walan ara, amek id Inezzu ร–ebbi lxelq, sinna, Ippales as. Ih, ayagi, i ร–ebbi, d ushil"
  29,20,"Ini: \"iniget di tmurt, walit amek id Inza lxelq. Sinna, ร–ebbi a d Iawi lxelq aneggaru. Ih, ร–ebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  29,21,Ikkat win i S ihwan; Ipรชunu $ef win i S ihwan. ยฃureS jebbu nnwen
  29,22,"Ur tesfunnugem, kunwi, di tmurt, ne$ deg igenni. Ur tesรขim, war ร–ebbi, bab ne$ asettaรด"